  "detailed_description": "<strong>Orbatron</strong> is an exciting game that will test your reflexes, focus, and spatial reasoning.<br>Collect orbs, chain combos, and develop strategies to master each unique level.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Action-packed, challenging gameplay<br></li><li>Five main gameplay modes - <strong>Cluster</strong>, <strong>Flight</strong>, <strong>Monolith</strong>, <strong>Special</strong>, and <strong>Endless</strong><br></li><li>Find Hidden Orbs to unlock Special Levels with unique gameplay mechanics<br></li><li>Gorgeous surreal & eclectic environments <br></li><li>Approachable for players of all ages and skill levels, yet highly challenging and competitive<br></li><li>99 Unique and challenging levels<br></li><li>Leaderboards and Achievements<br></li><li>Expansive soundtrack<br></li><li>Extremely fast load times<br></li><li>Currently Rated 4.9/5.0 in the Oculus Store</li></ul>",
